welcome_message_body: Welcome to Forest Lake, where the natural beauty of its lakes and forests will captivate you. Immerse yourself in our charming city and discover why it's known as the "Jewel of the Lakes." Enjoy your stay and explore all that Forest Lake has to offer!

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Anoka County-Blaine Airport handles all commercial flights and offers a variety of amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: For private and charter flights, the private terminal at Anoka County-Blaine Airport provides a comfortable and exclusive experience.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Downtown Airport serves domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Downtown Airport caters to private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Crystal Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Crystal Airport is reserved for private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Flying Cloud Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Flying Cloud Airport caters to private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The main terminal of Minneapolis - St. Paul International Airport, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: A smaller terminal primarily serving low-cost carriers and regional flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: This is the main terminal of Municipal Airport, where most domestic and international flights operate.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal is responsible for handling all cargo and freight shipments at Municipal Airport.

wifi.note: WiFi is available throughout the airport, but may require a password for access.
